  "3257780": {
    "name": "Your Story: Games with Death",
    "steam_appid": 3257780,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/90aa7973f8afe174783a0c8a6b63985c.webp?t=1771916769\" width=620 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your Story: Games with Death</strong> — 这是一款&quot;选择你的冒险&quot;类型的互动文字冒险游戏，在游戏中你就是剧情的创造者，通过选择自己的道路，每个决定都可能带来辉煌或导致悲剧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款文字冒险游戏，讲述了一个中世纪的年轻冒险家想要逃离家乡，前往未知的土地寻找冒险的故事。这些未知的土地充满了神秘、谜团和致命的危险。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/103404da8d456381ce6d9f0289762478.poster.avif?t=1771916769\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/103404da8d456381ce6d9f0289762478.webm?t=1771916769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/103404da8d456381ce6d9f0289762478.mp4?t=1771916769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >命运早已注定，死亡就在眼前，但你有足够的力量改变你的命运吗？你可以重写历史，改写结局。在这里，一切皆有可能，只有你自己知道最终的结局。你将有机会与死神玩一场游戏，按照自己的规则，避开它的陷阱，选择自己的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your Story: Games with Death</strong> — 这不仅仅是一场冒险游戏，更是一段由你决定的旅程。这是你的故事，由你亲手书写。你的故事将走向何方，是成为英雄的史诗，还是走向悲剧的终点，全由你决定。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/8f3126355f8b5ff55de75baddb859594.webp?t=1771916769\" width=620 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身一位永不停歇的冒险家，追寻着内心的渴望，乘风破浪，探索未知的海域，寻找更美好的生活。 穿越茂密的丛林，每一株灌木都可能潜藏着致命的危险。 在古老的废墟中穿行，古老的阴影苏醒，墙壁诉说着被遗忘的秘密。 积累财富，或是选择流浪。 在这个世界，你的每一步都走在生死边缘。 一旦失误，深渊将吞噬你<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/f4d8ff56852f02e15d9b7c3a86152bf1.poster.avif?t=1771916769\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/f4d8ff56852f02e15d9b7c3a86152bf1.webm?t=1771916769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/f4d8ff56852f02e15d9b7c3a86152bf1.mp4?t=1771916769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Your Story: Games with Death 的世界里，生命就是一场游戏，命运从未给你设限。你能否通过所有的考验，解开所有的谜团？还是会迷失其中，一无所获？你的未来掌握在你自己手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/03debe99480118590c42b05a4959bf06.webp?t=1771916769\" width=620 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的选择决定一切。一个充满谜团和秘密的世界等待着你，每一次选择都将带给你意想不到的冒险，可能让你饱受痛苦，也可能让你名利双收。这是一条荆棘之路，布满了痛苦、失落和艰难的抉择。记住，每一个行动都需要付出代价，而这个代价往往是生命<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/63713b73433ec0a1288a77eaf5313417.poster.avif?t=1771916769\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/63713b73433ec0a1288a77eaf5313417.webm?t=1771916769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/63713b73433ec0a1288a77eaf5313417.mp4?t=1771916769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏充满了意想不到的转折，让你时刻保持紧张。死亡如影随形，一旦你犯错，它就会毫不犹豫地将你吞噬。有时候，看似正确的选择反而会让你走向毁灭。这个世界残酷无情，死亡只是游戏的一部分，让你从错误中吸取教训。但胜利并不总是好事，失败也不总是坏事。一切取决于你的选择，而这些选择所带来的后果往往难以预料<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/174694e2bd9218e9792bef7af8c9b4b9.webp?t=1771916769\" width=620 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三种难度设置带来独一无二的游戏体验。简单模式让您尽情享受剧情，而困难模式则会让您时刻感受到死亡的威胁，成为对耐心的考验。只有幸运儿才能闯过重重难关，最终通关。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/974a9ab2ac42f6489a9d42008782bad9.webp?t=1771916769\" width=620 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好加入这场故事冒险，揭开 Your Story: Games with Death 的谜团了吗？<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/472b3129c26d8c79a1cef668a30efb06.poster.avif?t=1771916769\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/472b3129c26d8c79a1cef668a30efb06.webm?t=1771916769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257780/extras/472b3129c26d8c79a1cef668a30efb06.mp4?t=1771916769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加到愿望清单，不要错过这个激动人心的故事！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
